data.title: Świętosława «Gunhilda» "Świętosława «Gunhilda» Piast Mieszkówna" Mieszkówna (± 955
data.meta_description: Świętosława «Gunhilda» Mieszkówna was born about 955 in Götaland, daughter of Mieszko I and Doubravka Dobrawa Przemyślida., they had 2 children. She died on February  2, 1014. This information is part of Family tree Den Hollander en Van Dueren den Hollander by Kees den Hollander on Genealogy Online.
